title: Nursery Interview
Application Type: I applied in-person. The process took 1 day. I interviewed at The Village Church (Baldwin, WI) in Feb 2014
Interview Descriptions: The interview was easy and informative of the job I would be doing.  The intervieweres seemed very nice and told me a lot of the church and the kids.  All the parents are nice and kind to work with.  IF I had conflicts with the schedule it was easy to resolve
